\id PHM  
\h Filemon 
\toc1 Filemon 
\toc2 Filemon 
\toc3 Filemon 
\mt1 Filemon  
\ip Filemon di de nla' oleka Kristen ne edonna nhal de e' ed mak kla oleka krei mutnu la Kolose. Atni ida de nwawa Onisimus. La' hadom pede atni di nawlar dioinia la. La' hadoma rerieini pa atni de nora Paulus rwatamputu la'a roma nhio'la ralamni. La'a Paulus hihi'ini pa Onisimus (at de), nler olek la agama Kristen.  
\ip Horat di ed maka Paulus na'enyat lia Filemon totpena na nwak la pa Filemon nor Onisimus rkalwieda. Paulus nwak pa Filemon yana nhi' yatyat la, mere nwayow pa na' owa'an la Onisimus mak ha nwa'at de. Ne yana Filemon nhoratnana to'a e atni pa nora rkalwieda, mere yoma Filemon nhorat nan Onisimus di nor rewre'wa e' pa rhi' riy mak la oleka riy Kristen ira.  
\is1 La' puka di de e rakot nohor emkadille:  
\io2 1. Mulaliaini (1:3)  
\io2 2. Filemon pesiayni nora kalwiedni (1:4-7)  
\io2 3. Wniaka la Onisimus (1:8-22)  
\io2 4. Lira kniowni (1:23-25)  
\c 1  
\s1 Paulus nwak kalwieda  
\p
\v 1 Heiwia'lu Filemon! Paulus a' di mak katnioran la roma nhio'la ralamni yoma la'a Kristus Yesus tulanni-kniarni, me it hyalli Timotius, amro'a ama'enyatga horat di tiy heiwia'lu mak kden la a ralam mamni, mak kor am pia mkar wiutu,  
\v 2 me la' walia ita kreiwialli mak kahniopun rer lia' rommu nayanni. Me ami edonna mhortaplin wualia it narni Aphia nor it heiwialli Arkhipus mak emekwali ami, pa emeka mak ka'ara ida, natu ntutulu-nlelewua nniahora-nniala'a la' Uplerlawna kniarni ralamni.   
\p
\v 3 Ampak de Uplerlawna it Amlawanni de, nora Itmatromni Yesus Kristus, pena ed mak kala ra'ani-pallu me kalwieda-paitiota tiy miy.   
\s1 Filemon hmuakarnu nodia yara'a-yapalu  
\p
\v 4 Heiwia'lu Filemon, la' a sniumbainu lelera-melmel de a'u'uli-uwed reri Uplerlawna mak akola tieru-gawur nehla de.  
\v 5 Yoma la' a yatli'nu de, o' e muhmuakur toto' la pesiaymu la Itmatromlawanni Yesus, ne muatu mtiulla-msiayn walia mutlialawna mak kla' olek la Uplerlawna mutnu.  
\v 6 Awuak la Uplerlawna totpena onnila o pesiaymu la' Yesus me la' walia omnia'erit nan memna it rurni-laini ra'ani-pallu re honona mak Uplerlawna Nara'a-napalga mai ita, pede hota omuora makpesiay re yeher to' pa mlia' ihru ida-ralm ida. La' talan emkade pede Uplerlawna Nlernana ya'uli-yawedi la makpesiay E'a. \f + \fr 1.6 \ft 1:6 Riy dom de rwarora ayat di nnia'eratni emkadi: Asiumbaini totpena yeher to' pa omor makpesiay mlia' ihru ida-ralm ida me totpena muat niohora yara'a-yapalu honona maka Uplerlawna Nala mai ita, totpena hota riy ra'uli-rawedi Uplerlawna. \f*  
\v 7 Heiwia'lu Filemon, la'a yara'amu-yapalmu la mutlialawna mak kler olek la Uplerlawna mutnu pepanni-taurnu ralamni re de, nrei a lia hepur lawna ne nod wiali a' pua a hmuakru naruri owa'an la genni, yoma la' o hihi'imu-yapyapmu mak kareiniande riy mak kler olek la Uplerlawna limni ralamni rahepur wenna.   
\s1 Paulus nwak pa Filemon nreiniana atni-wa'arni Onisimus pa emeka hyalli id la pesiay ida  
\p
\v 8-9 Heiwia'lu, agatga de onnila a' di de maka Yesus Nhopan pa godia Uplerlawna Kot Kalwiedni, de agodi plolli pa aghopna heiwia'lu nhi'a hya' maka hota mhi'a. Mere emkade ho'mana onnila' mtiulla-msiayni la mutlialawna makpesiay re pede awuak to' tiy o'a. Awuak lilili-mamuau tiy o'a, totpa mrieiniana-mua'nana a li'ru di. A' di de hamtoto' olek a'u ne mumkek memna de a'g ed ma'ta la roma nhio'la ralamni onnila Kristus Yesus lirni-tunnu.  
\v 10 Heiwia'lu, ukota ralma-rio'ru di tiy o'a la' a a'nu. Meman neka la e' de a a'nu raralma atia'a mere la roma nhio'la ralamni di a'g ed maka ukot nohora mormiori-dardiari warwuaru la e'a, ne dodo'ondi npesiay walia pede enhi' a a'nu la it pesiayni di. Muat niohora olek e' wali yoma nanni de Onisimus (maka nnia'eratni de nperkuna).  
\v 11 Ululu omuora atmu Onisimus di mdien wut die, edon nodia unut tiy o'a. Mere la' lera-mela ri, de hota edon nodia unut la o' mueh'a, mere hota nperkun matmiat mai itro'a.  
\v 12 La'pa dodo'ondi de Onisimus di maka a ralmu nal de, de aghopan pa nawalia owa'an tiy o'a.   
\p
\v 13 La' a wniareknu de agiwa ultarga totpena nwaug o'a pa nhi'inde nhima-nre' a lia'a a knia'ru di, la ler mak adien ma'ta la roma nhio'la ralamni onnila a'ukot nohora Uplerlawna Kot Kalwiedni.  
\v 14 Mere a'g edonna get mia'ta la hadomdoma, yoma heiwia'lu edonna nakot ma'ta ralma-riorni. Awuak lilili-mamuau tiy o'a, totpena mueh'a mhuria ralammu ne yana atiekga o'a.  
\v 15 Mere yanpa Uplerlawna Nolin doinia Onisimus olieta-patoga tiy o' di, de, edonna nodia la wenu-wolla, totpena npesiay Itmatromni Yesus pa hota omual owa'an e'a pa la'pa mmuati-mmuor niohora edon ntut tio'ola nohkeran di, mere la' pa ntut mueman la Ilyamou-Watyatoha pa nodi liarni.  
\v 16 Lera-mela de hota nwehwa-nlakat tiy o' de edon emeka atmu-wa'armu to'a mere hota wniehwani-liakatni tiy o' de kalwiedni narehi owa'an la hade, yoma hota e' de, de nor o' pa mpia'ama-mpiahyal lia' pesiay ida. E' de nden nek la a ralmu ne meman neka la hota reriehenu pa o ralammu nal walia e'a, emeka atmu-wa'armu me emekwalima riy mak kwa'ama-kwahyali, kwa'ina-kwanar la' Itmatromlawanni.   
\p
\v 17 La' hade pede la'pa ompuarora heiwialmu a lia la' it pesiayni, me kniar wialmu la Uplerlawna kniarni ralamni, de awuak de mrieinian owa'ana Onisimus pa emekwalia o e mrieinian a'u.  
\v 18 Ne la'pa e nhala, onde e nhi' nana otna-ar tiy o'a, de pena a'g ed maka khernu-kwauga tiy o'a.  
\v 19 La'pa emkade nek wa, ne amueh'a kenia la handi, Paulus a orgah'u hadi, pena hota aghernu-wuaga otna-ara re honona. Hota a'g edonna wuahniort la'a o' nek de yanpa o' e mu'otan mai a'u. La'a nnia'eratni de, o' ed mak kwaka terima kasi lawlawan mai a'u, yoma omlia' oleka makpesiay.  
\v 20 Heiwia'lu awuak owa'an pa mtiultulan pa mrieiniana Onisimus. Mrieiniana a wakwa'ku di pa emeka twa'ina-twanara la Yesus Kristus loini-talanni, totpena hota la' hihi'imu-yapyapmu de pa alier la ralma hepuepru onnila itla' id la Yesus Kristus.  
\v 21 Aghi'a horat di de a ralmu napranrana, yoma agatga de hota heiwia'lu nreiniana hya' maka awuaka. Nareh wiali die, agatga de hota heiwia'lu nhi'a de reh wial hade.   
\p
\v 22 Ne awuak walia hadi tiy o'a, de pena mtiulan pa muhgalia o rommu kamarni id mai a'u, yoma agha'ar a arnu la Uplerlawna de hota la' miy sniumbainmi re, ed mak kottiarg owa'an a lia miy hononmi.   
\s1 Lir kalwieda hohoni  
\p
\v 23 Epafras e nor a lia'a roma nhio'la, yoma la'a Kristus Yesus rerieini. E' wal pia e nwak kalwieda tiy o'a.  
\v 24 Me a kniarwia'lu Markus, Aristarkus, Demas, me Lukas e ra'enyat wut lir kalwiedni tiy o'a.   
\p
\v 25 A honon ampak de Itmatromlawanni Yesus Kristus Nala ra'ani-pallu nanaloi-nanatar nan miy.  
\p A honon kalwied mamni,  
\p Paulus   